PN,37901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782728295
OL,3,CPE kits, water bottles and European
OL,4,Ctimetables to help schools cope in the
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FSome schools are changing the
OL,8,Ftimetable to help children cope with
OL,9,Fthe heat. Pupils are allowed to arrive
OL,10,Fand leave earlier as temperatures soar
OL,11,Ftowards 40 Celsius.
OL,13,FLights are being turned off and water
OL,14,Fbottles and PE kits are helping
OL,15,Fclassrooms deal with extreme
OL,16,Ftemperatures.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782728295
OL,3,CPE kits, water bottles and European
OL,4,Ctimetables to help schools cope in the
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,F"All the children have come to school
OL,8,Fin their PE kits today, they all have
OL,9,Fwater bottles on their table that
OL,10,Fthey're using throughout the day,"
OL,11,Fsaid Elizabeth Harris, Headteacher at
OL,12,FMonega Primary School in east London.
OL,14,F"We have no lights on in the
OL,15,Fclassrooms, which is obviously a
OL,16,Flittle bit different, but children
OL,17,Fhave accommodated and worked really
OL,18,Fwell with that.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782728295
OL,3,CPE kits, water bottles and European
OL,4,Ctimetables to help schools cope in the
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,F"It is definitely really hot and it's
OL,8,Funusual, but we put in provisions. So
OL,9,Fchildren all have a water bottle on
OL,10,Ftheir table.
OL,12,F"They've all come to school much
OL,13,Fearlier than they normally would and
OL,14,Fthey'll be leaving much earlier than
OL,15,Fthey normally would.
OL,17,F"So we've kind of gone for a European
OL,18,Ftimetable and I think whether this is
OL,19,Fepisodic or whether it becomes a
OL,20,Fpattern, I think people will kind of
OL,21,Fwatch and see.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782728295
OL,3,CPE kits, water bottles and European
OL,4,Ctimetables to help schools cope in the
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,F"Aircon is obviously really
OL,8,Fbeneficial. You can work much more
OL,9,Feffectively when it's very hot, but I
OL,10,Fthink that would be much further along
OL,11,Fthe line if this became a common
OL,12,Fpattern," Elizabeth Harris explained.
OL,14,FWednesday and Thursday's red warning
OL,15,Ffrom the Met Office for extreme heat
OL,16,Fmeans temperatures potentially
OL,17,Fclimbing as high as 40C.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
