PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782728295
OL,3,CPE kits, water bottles and European
OL,4,Ctimetables to help schools cope in the
OL,5,Cheat
OL,7,FForecasters have also issued an amber
OL,8,Fwarning for heat on Friday, covering
OL,9,Fmuch of England, with the hottest
OL,10,Fspots potentially peaking around 38C
OL,11,Fin eastern and central areas.
OL,13,FAnd with the extreme heat set to
OL,14,Flinger in some parts of the country
OL,15,Finto the weekend, the Met Office has
OL,16,Fissued an amber warning for extreme
OL,17,Fheat covering parts of east and south-
OL,18,Feast England on Saturday.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
